Locale-Maketext-TieHash-nbsp version 1.02
=========================================

Subroutines don't have interpreted into strings.
The module ties the subroutine to change blanks in protected blanks to a hash.
The subroutine is executed at fetch hash.
At long last this is the same, only the notation is shorter.


INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install

Alternatively, to install with Module::Build, you can use the following commands:

    perl Build.PL
    ./Build
    ./Build test
    ./Build install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Tie::Sub
  Params::Validate

